@startuml Training + Heatmap Sequence

skinparam backgroundColor #030712
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #60a5fa
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #3b82f6
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #1f2937
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #3b82f6
skinparam fontColor #f9fafb

== Training Flow ==

actor User
participant "React Frontend" as FE
participant "FastAPI /train" as API
participant "BackgroundTask\n(Trainer)" as BG
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Filesystem\n(weights/)" as FS

User -> FE: Click "Uruchom trening"\n(epochs=200, lr=0.001, layers=[64,32])
FE -> API: POST /api/train
API -> DB: INSERT model_runs\nstatus="training"
DB --> API: run_id=42
API --> FE: {run_id: 42, status: "training"}
API -> BG: BackgroundTask.add_task(train_model, run_id=42)

loop every 2 seconds
    FE -> API: GET /api/train/42/status
    API -> BG: read TRAINING_STATE[42]
    API --> FE: {current_epoch, loss, r2_score}
    FE -> FE: Update LossChart
end

BG -> BG: Forward pass + backprop\n(batch_size=32, Adam optimizer)
BG -> FS: torch.save({weights, stats}, "weights/42.pt")
BG -> DB: UPDATE model_runs\nstatus="done", mse_loss, r2_score
FE -> FE: Auto-select model 42

== Heatmap Request Flow ==

User -> FE: Move slider (area_m2=60)
FE -> FE: Debounce 300ms
FE -> API: POST /api/heatmap\n{run_id:42, resolution:100, area_m2:60, ...}
API -> DB: SELECT model_runs WHERE id=42
API -> FS: torch.load("weights/42.pt")
API -> API: Build 100×100 lat/lon grid\nRun 10,000 forward passes
API -> API: PIL.Image → base64 PNG
API --> FE: {image_base64, min_val, max_val, bounds}
FE -> FE: L.imageOverlay.setUrl(data:image/png;base64,...)
FE -> User: Heatmap updated on Leaflet map

== OAuth Flow ==

User -> FE: Click "Zaloguj przez Google"
FE -> API: GET /auth/google
API --> User: Redirect → Google consent screen
User -> API: GET /auth/google/callback?code=...
API -> API: Authlib exchange code for token
API -> DB: UPSERT users (email, provider_id)
API -> API: Create JWT (HS256)
API --> FE: Redirect /admin?token=<jwt>
FE -> FE: localStorage.setItem("auth_token", jwt)
FE -> API: GET /auth/me (Bearer <jwt>)
API --> FE: {email, name, picture, role}

@enduml
